sg":"可唔可以講詳細啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"隻藥就未香港註冊之前上過appledaily,所以都係經大陸手，價錢方面就問下上面班巴絲好d,因為我唔知自己有冇比人食咗好多。<br />\n<br />\n咁我果隻都係一個月大無啦啦左右肚好脹，唔食野無精神，飲好多水，咁就見醫生話9成係，咁就上Fb揾group買藥，上面有好清楚q&amp;a比你，之後就要晚晚打針，同埋個個月驗血，通常會根情況停針，但都係問醫生意見，之後要買一堆補品同埋AD罐頭比佢食，洗好多錢，但生命唔可以用錢去衡量，你養得佢就要負責任，多多錢都值，比個數你，最小15k。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVNtjbtaocmjzrqRRtRvkmAjjs6gCEmYxCwsmF5h7spi6?filename=B3G5FkA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3G5FkA.png&h=87241db7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeQ3Y6SehfAFb5pmGjSJdx4F7GTSdfBUWjNoJ69rPtrzu?filename=jfxAh7r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjfxAh7r.png&h=8b4aa2a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddca13de77ce5deeef1b02ec4834b6ef20c20cec","tid":2499251,"uid":223963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6525fc95b0dc0920d888d6877f65e74810509fb","tid":2499251,"uid":369954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb4a28ec28ed9bfcd3993c767a78614e71b67971","tid":2499251,"uid":223963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:04:42.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<br />\n<br />\n之前我都有兩隻細貓腹膜炎就死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:25:05.000Z","msg":"腹膜炎真係睇到佢地都肉赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T12:57:02.000Z","msg":"傷心到我 <br />\n望住一隻接一隻走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295d725456bb3a63600d6cec143013c8f2886135","tid":2499251,"uid":223963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04e919f35690582032242c9ea65de7229e4a9c6c","tid":2499251,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb4a28ec28ed9bfcd3993c767a78614e71b67971","tid":2499251,"uid":223963,"lik